[section#thread.mutex.general
    [:en] General
    [:zh_CN] 概述
]

[para]
[:en] Subclause [#thread.mutex] provides mechanisms for mutual exclusion:
mutexes, locks, and call once.
[:zh_CN] 子条款 [#thread.mutex] 提供互斥的几种机制：互斥体、锁和单次调用。

[:en] These mechanisms ease the production of race-free programs
([#intro.multithread]).
[:zh_CN] 这些机制简化了编写免除数据竞争的程序的工作（[#intro.multithread]）。
